1
00:00:30,250 --> 00:00:34,965
♪Through dust and storms,
I press on alone♪

2
00:00:36,330 --> 00:00:39,202
♪Winds arise,
sands stretch far and wide♪

3
00:00:39,271 --> 00:00:41,982
♪Trials of the world test my resolve♪

4
00:00:42,127 --> 00:00:46,625
♪Forged in fire,
I chase the light beyond♪

5
00:00:47,630 --> 00:00:51,042
♪Facing challenges, fate ever shifts♪

6
00:00:51,260 --> 00:00:54,959
♪A journey
through the wilderness of time♪

7
00:00:54,960 --> 00:01:00,684
♪Fearless like armor,
through thorns I grow♪

8
00:01:00,760 --> 00:01:05,256
♪Breaking through darkness,
my name will shine♪

9
00:01:05,560 --> 00:01:07,540
♪Never in vain♪

10
00:01:08,370 --> 00:01:13,660
♪Guarding my fleeting light,
tempered to shine bright♪

11
00:01:14,444 --> 00:01:15,860
♪Cherished past♪

12
00:01:16,008 --> 00:01:20,491
♪A lifetime treasured,
through a thousand waves we ride♪

13
00:01:20,728 --> 00:01:23,937
♪To fight with fury,
to love with passion♪

14
00:01:23,943 --> 00:01:26,465
♪True to my faith♪

15
00:01:26,503 --> 00:01:31,964
♪I greet the frost
and the prize with pride♪

16
00:01:32,700 --> 00:01:36,040
=Love and Sword=

17
00:01:36,040 --> 00:01:40,480
(Adapted from Shen Cangmei's novel
Sleeping Beside Yan Shao)

18
00:01:41,620 --> 00:01:44,010
=Episode 7=

19
00:01:53,960 --> 00:01:54,850
It's getting windy.

20
00:01:55,960 --> 00:01:59,770
The spring breeze
brings the fallen flowers.

21
00:02:01,240 --> 00:02:02,010
Tomorrow night,

22
00:02:02,520 --> 00:02:04,320
I'm afraid the street will be too full

23
00:02:04,720 --> 00:02:06,360
of fallen flowers to be swept away.

24
00:02:06,770 --> 00:02:07,570
Fallen flowers?

25
00:02:07,671 --> 00:02:09,160
They deserve such a nice description?

26
00:02:09,426 --> 00:02:11,370
They're nothing more
than a bunch of pissants.

27
00:02:12,426 --> 00:02:14,715
In all my years of traveling
in the martial world,

28
00:02:14,850 --> 00:02:15,920
I've never seen

29
00:02:15,920 --> 00:02:17,690
a woman like you.

30
00:02:18,090 --> 00:02:21,250
You're so weak but ruthless.

31
00:02:21,671 --> 00:02:24,582
The martial world is full of strife,
and only the strongest survive.

32
00:02:25,293 --> 00:02:27,715
Which of those who claim
to be of the highest caliber

33
00:02:27,850 --> 00:02:29,290
are not motivated by greed?

34
00:02:30,200 --> 00:02:31,480
If it weren't for the treasure,

35
00:02:31,920 --> 00:02:33,760
they all wouldn't be here.

36
00:02:34,640 --> 00:02:35,920
If something happens

37
00:02:36,090 --> 00:02:38,640
to those sects in the territory
of Yuchi Manor,

38
00:02:39,090 --> 00:02:41,850
it will be difficult for Master Lin
to explain to the world.

39
00:02:42,493 --> 00:02:44,810
Since ancient times,
the weak have submitted to the strong.

40
00:02:45,570 --> 00:02:47,600
The strong don't care
what the weak think.

41
00:02:48,760 --> 00:02:49,850
By the time Yuchi Manor

42
00:02:49,850 --> 00:02:51,530
rules the martial arts world,

43
00:02:52,160 --> 00:02:53,640
they won't have the guts to complain.

44
00:02:54,640 --> 00:02:56,250
If you weren't in such a state,

45
00:02:56,600 --> 00:02:59,600
you'd have the whole Yuchi Manor
in your possession.

46
00:03:00,480 --> 00:03:02,130
If I wasn't in such a state,

47
00:03:04,010 --> 00:03:05,320
I wouldn't need others

48
00:03:05,320 --> 00:03:06,920
to help me plan.

49
00:03:11,410 --> 00:03:12,010
It's all right.

50
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:15,600
With your body,

51
00:03:15,850 --> 00:03:17,760
you can't withstand the spring breeze.

52
00:03:18,515 --> 00:03:19,880
The great work is not yet done.

53
00:03:20,880 --> 00:03:21,970
I won't die yet.

54
00:03:31,880 --> 00:03:33,160
Where did you go, Young Lady Lin?

55
00:03:33,480 --> 00:03:34,720
Are you here to see me?

56
00:03:35,137 --> 00:03:37,760
Young Master Lin and Young Lady Rong
are worried about you.

57
00:03:38,480 --> 00:03:39,600
I was just walking around.

58
00:03:39,760 --> 00:03:40,480
Let's go back.

59
00:03:40,850 --> 00:03:41,320
Okay.

60
00:04:10,204 --> 00:04:12,693
(Yuchi Manor)
The Pure Sword Sect has arrived.

61
00:04:13,130 --> 00:04:14,440
The Tang Clan has arrived.

62
00:04:14,810 --> 00:04:16,080
The Spirit Fox Sect has arrived.

63
00:04:16,080 --> 00:04:17,200
Madam Xing, this way, please.

64
00:04:17,280 --> 00:04:18,690
The Junshan Sect has arrived.

65
00:04:18,690 --> 00:04:19,560
Madam Xing.

66
00:04:20,510 --> 00:04:21,310
(Madam Xing,)

67
00:04:21,310 --> 00:04:22,930
(Head of Pure Sword Sect)
It's been a long time.

68
00:04:22,937 --> 00:04:24,570
You're still so strong and healthy.

69
00:04:25,490 --> 00:04:27,690
You haven't been out for years,

70
00:04:28,080 --> 00:04:30,130
and now you're in Yuchi Manor in person.

71
00:04:30,810 --> 00:04:32,610
Master Lin has so much respect.

72
00:04:33,440 --> 00:04:34,080
Head Tang.

73
00:04:34,114 --> 00:04:35,460
(Tang Chanyi, Head of Tang Clan)

74
00:04:36,048 --> 00:04:38,130
(A Disciple of Junshan Sect)
Is Head Tang thinking of

75
00:04:38,130 --> 00:04:39,880
forming a marriage bond
with Yuchi Manor?

76
00:04:39,960 --> 00:04:40,520
What?

77
00:04:41,050 --> 00:04:43,250
Your sect is afraid
of Ghost Valley Sect

78
00:04:43,250 --> 00:04:44,893
and even your head doesn't dare to come?

79
00:04:44,937 --> 00:04:46,520
The Seven-Star Hall has arrived.

80
00:04:48,610 --> 00:04:50,640
Chanyi, don't be mad at him.

81
00:04:51,311 --> 00:04:53,690
(Jiang Ruhai, Seven-Star Hall)

82
00:04:54,382 --> 00:04:55,280
Chief Jiang.

83
00:04:55,820 --> 00:04:57,782
(Jiang Cheng, Chief of Seven-Star Hall)
Head Tang,

84
00:04:57,826 --> 00:04:59,290
how have you been?

85
00:04:59,448 --> 00:05:00,471
I have been good.

86
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,626
That's good to hear.

87
00:05:07,637 --> 00:05:11,010
(Boardroom)

88
00:05:14,810 --> 00:05:16,893
You all have traveled
across the seas or mountains

89
00:05:17,250 --> 00:05:19,010
to join us here at Yuchi Manor.

90
00:05:19,520 --> 00:05:21,640
I'm deeply grateful.

91
00:05:24,840 --> 00:05:26,440
I apologize for the poor hospitality.

92
00:05:26,930 --> 00:05:28,080
Please forgive that.

93
00:05:28,280 --> 00:05:29,130
Master Lin,

94
00:05:29,690 --> 00:05:31,690
spare the formalities.

95
00:05:32,760 --> 00:05:34,690
We came to Yuchi Manor

96
00:05:35,250 --> 00:05:38,320
for the sake of Six Great Sects
to be together

97
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:40,440
and to support each other.

98
00:05:42,170 --> 00:05:42,730
Wait.

99
00:05:43,610 --> 00:05:45,490
If it's a war
with Ghost Valley Sect,

100
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:48,440
the Pure Sword Sect
doesn't intend to be part of it.

101
00:05:49,320 --> 00:05:50,490
That's what

102
00:05:50,840 --> 00:05:53,050
we're here to discuss.

103
00:05:53,490 --> 00:05:54,130
Master Lin,

104
00:05:55,250 --> 00:05:57,010
Ghost Valley Sect arrested someone

105
00:05:57,320 --> 00:06:02,010
for the key and map
to the Fuxian treasure.

106
00:06:08,170 --> 00:06:09,760
Who here

107
00:06:09,760 --> 00:06:11,130
isn't after the treasure?

108
00:06:12,648 --> 00:06:15,050
Today, I'd like to ask
Master Lin for an explanation.

109
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:18,610
Is the key to the treasure
in Yuchi Manor or not?

110
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:25,170
I've invited you here,

111
00:06:25,610 --> 00:06:28,200
firstly for Zhonghe Festival,

112
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,293
and secondly,

113
00:06:29,930 --> 00:06:32,320
to discuss this matter.

114
00:06:32,930 --> 00:06:34,130
You've come a long way,

115
00:06:34,137 --> 00:06:35,560
so why don't you take a rest first?

116
00:06:36,050 --> 00:06:37,520
As for this matter, it's not urgent.

117
00:06:37,737 --> 00:06:39,130
We can discuss it in the long run.

118
00:06:42,280 --> 00:06:43,960
Master, the guest rooms are ready.

119
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:46,280
Please have a good rest.

120
00:06:47,440 --> 00:06:48,370
Please come with me.

121
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:49,930
Please.

122
00:06:50,880 --> 00:06:51,280
Please.

123
00:06:54,280 --> 00:06:55,280
You've disgraced

124
00:06:55,440 --> 00:06:56,810
the Tang family.

125
00:06:57,690 --> 00:06:59,400
Chanyi, what's wrong?

126
00:06:59,520 --> 00:07:01,400
You've been following
Lin Shaoci all day.

127
00:07:01,400 --> 00:07:02,448
It's been so many years

128
00:07:02,471 --> 00:07:03,915
and he hasn't married you yet.

129
00:07:05,130 --> 00:07:06,200
If you go on like this,

130
00:07:06,810 --> 00:07:09,130
you'll become the laughing stock
sooner or later,

131
00:07:09,370 --> 00:07:11,130
just like Rong Shukuang
and Yu Linglong.

132
00:07:12,130 --> 00:07:13,520
Brother Shaoci has his own plans.

133
00:07:13,610 --> 00:07:15,026
Snake, be good.

134
00:07:17,610 --> 00:07:18,130
Use this

135
00:07:18,826 --> 00:07:20,848
and he will definitely fall for you.

136
00:07:24,320 --> 00:07:27,490
Chanyi, I can't do this
to someone I like.

137
00:07:37,760 --> 00:07:39,760
Distribute the people in the inner city

138
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:41,640
to coordinate with each other

139
00:07:42,170 --> 00:07:43,440
to protect the city.

140
00:07:44,840 --> 00:07:45,520
So

141
00:07:46,050 --> 00:07:47,640
the city will be well protected

142
00:07:48,610 --> 00:07:49,690
and there'll be no mistakes.

143
00:07:50,520 --> 00:07:51,080
Father,

144
00:07:52,010 --> 00:07:53,400
the sects are gathering today.

145
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:56,320
The heads and chiefs
have their own plans, right?

146
00:07:56,930 --> 00:07:58,400
Whether it's a friend or foe,

147
00:07:58,810 --> 00:08:00,880
we can't give Ghost Valley Sect

148
00:08:01,400 --> 00:08:03,050
a chance to take advantage of us.

149
00:08:03,810 --> 00:08:04,400
I understood.

150
00:08:04,730 --> 00:08:05,250
Besides,

151
00:08:06,080 --> 00:08:08,810
there's one more thing
you should plan as soon as possible.

152
00:08:10,130 --> 00:08:12,960
For Yu Linglong and Tang Yingluo...

153
00:08:13,626 --> 00:08:14,960
Which one...

154
00:08:16,640 --> 00:08:18,130
do you want to marry?

155
00:08:20,520 --> 00:08:21,050
Father,

156
00:08:21,440 --> 00:08:22,730
Yu and Yingluo,

157
00:08:23,280 --> 00:08:23,930
to me,

158
00:08:24,610 --> 00:08:25,730
are sisters like Wanci.

159
00:08:27,370 --> 00:08:28,930
Sisters?

160
00:08:29,080 --> 00:08:31,080
They are not your blood relatives.

161
00:08:31,730 --> 00:08:32,800
How can they be the same?

162
00:08:33,515 --> 00:08:34,730
What about Shukuang?

163
00:08:35,850 --> 00:08:36,490
You said

164
00:08:37,400 --> 00:08:39,520
you just thought
of Shukuang as a sister.

165
00:08:40,160 --> 00:08:41,330
- To her, you...
- Father.

166
00:08:41,880 --> 00:08:43,130
Once upon a time, I even thought

167
00:08:44,400 --> 00:08:45,520
that Shukuang was a man

168
00:08:46,490 --> 00:08:48,130
I could trust and rely on.

169
00:08:48,880 --> 00:08:49,560
But

170
00:08:50,250 --> 00:08:51,520
since she got hurt,

171
00:08:52,560 --> 00:08:54,160
I feel like she's changed.

172
00:08:56,490 --> 00:08:57,210
I suddenly...

173
00:08:57,448 --> 00:08:59,648
Suddenly, I feel like
I want to protect her.

174
00:09:03,160 --> 00:09:03,640
Father,

175
00:09:04,250 --> 00:09:04,970
I still need

176
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:06,400
to think about this.

177
00:09:06,800 --> 00:09:08,370
Two days later is Zhonghe Festival.

178
00:09:08,693 --> 00:09:10,293
It is not to be taken lightly.

179
00:09:11,093 --> 00:09:12,137
You may leave now.

180
00:09:12,920 --> 00:09:13,400
Yes.

181
00:09:42,893 --> 00:09:44,210
Watch out, Young Lady Rong.

182
00:09:46,330 --> 00:09:46,730
Let's go.

183
00:09:49,730 --> 00:09:51,250
You finally showed up.

184
00:09:51,560 --> 00:09:52,730
I haven't seen you all day.

185
00:09:53,040 --> 00:09:54,160
Where have you been?

186
00:09:54,640 --> 00:09:55,450
Drinking.

187
00:09:55,850 --> 00:09:58,280
Drinking on such an important day?

188
00:10:01,610 --> 00:10:02,040
Fine.

189
00:10:02,093 --> 00:10:03,293
As long as you're back.

190
00:10:04,040 --> 00:10:04,850
Look at me.

191
00:10:05,730 --> 00:10:06,920
What do you think?

192
00:10:16,400 --> 00:10:18,880
You deserve the title
of Top Swordsman of Yuchi Manor.

193
00:10:21,970 --> 00:10:22,520
Go.

194
00:10:55,520 --> 00:10:56,610
Greetings, Master Lin.

195
00:10:57,010 --> 00:10:57,450
Head Yu,

196
00:10:57,680 --> 00:10:58,160
Madam Xing.

197
00:10:58,330 --> 00:11:00,280
Today's flower fair is very lively.

198
00:11:00,280 --> 00:11:00,730
Yes.

199
00:11:00,920 --> 00:11:02,250
Today is Zhonghe Festival.

200
00:11:02,330 --> 00:11:04,250
We are honored to have

201
00:11:04,370 --> 00:11:05,450
all the heroes here.

202
00:11:05,610 --> 00:11:07,560
Whoever wins the contest

203
00:11:07,560 --> 00:11:08,671
against all the other heroes

204
00:11:08,680 --> 00:11:11,610
will be rewarded
with a big gift from Yuchi Manor.

205
00:11:15,920 --> 00:11:17,090
Young Lady Rong, I'm here.

206
00:11:20,450 --> 00:11:21,040
She...

207
00:11:23,040 --> 00:11:23,680
Let's go.

208
00:11:23,680 --> 00:11:25,010
After two hours,

209
00:11:25,970 --> 00:11:27,160
the Red Banner Flower Fair

210
00:11:27,490 --> 00:11:28,400
will officially begin.

211
00:11:28,760 --> 00:11:29,640
Please have a seat.

212
00:11:30,010 --> 00:11:30,450
Please.

213
00:11:36,610 --> 00:11:38,450
I thought I won every year.

214
00:11:38,760 --> 00:11:39,800
What about my prize money?

215
00:11:40,760 --> 00:11:43,250
The prize money is for this year,
not for previous years.

216
00:11:43,737 --> 00:11:45,271
- That's too unfair.
- Mister and Miss,

217
00:11:45,293 --> 00:11:45,960
please come in.

218
00:11:45,982 --> 00:11:47,640
I'll bring you a bottle of good wine.

219
00:11:48,250 --> 00:11:48,450
Okay.

220
00:11:48,450 --> 00:11:48,970
Have a seat.

221
00:11:50,800 --> 00:11:51,800
Young Lady Rong,

222
00:11:52,130 --> 00:11:53,040
it's been a long time.

223
00:11:53,970 --> 00:11:55,210
I'm glad

224
00:11:55,610 --> 00:11:56,800
to see you're safe and sound.

225
00:11:57,560 --> 00:11:58,520
Young Master Ruhai,

226
00:11:58,920 --> 00:12:00,560
Young Lady Rong has been missing you.

227
00:12:00,560 --> 00:12:01,210
Yes.

228
00:12:01,248 --> 00:12:02,090
She broke your leg

229
00:12:02,090 --> 00:12:03,760
at the flower fair last year.

230
00:12:04,250 --> 00:12:05,490
She's still upset about that.

231
00:12:06,400 --> 00:12:07,250
How's your leg?

232
00:12:07,370 --> 00:12:08,010
Thank you.

233
00:12:08,450 --> 00:12:09,010
It's healed.

234
00:12:09,130 --> 00:12:11,610
Well, was I ever this mean?

235
00:12:12,880 --> 00:12:15,850
Is your leg okay
for this year's contest?

236
00:12:16,520 --> 00:12:17,250
This one.

237
00:12:19,404 --> 00:12:19,920
Okay.

238
00:12:20,450 --> 00:12:22,640
If my guard wins
the prize money this year,

239
00:12:22,730 --> 00:12:23,730
I'll give you all of it

240
00:12:23,730 --> 00:12:25,210
as medical expenses.

241
00:12:25,210 --> 00:12:25,850
Okay?

242
00:12:25,850 --> 00:12:27,330
I don't care about money.

243
00:12:27,360 --> 00:12:28,730
If you really want to apologize,

244
00:12:29,250 --> 00:12:29,730
come on,

245
00:12:32,560 --> 00:12:33,760
drink up this bowl of wine

246
00:12:33,760 --> 00:12:34,680
as an apology.

247
00:12:35,250 --> 00:12:36,010
I'll finish it.

248
00:12:37,970 --> 00:12:38,730
Young Lady Rong,

249
00:12:39,010 --> 00:12:41,160
you're the best of men,
and the greatest of women.

250
00:12:41,370 --> 00:12:42,370
Here's to you.

251
00:12:42,920 --> 00:12:44,210
- You flatter me.
- Yan Shao.

252
00:12:44,210 --> 00:12:45,330
- Let's drink.
- Bottoms up.

253
00:12:45,330 --> 00:12:47,350
Young Lady Lin told you
to prepare for the contest.

254
00:12:47,400 --> 00:12:47,730
Okay.

255
00:12:47,804 --> 00:12:49,404
- Young Lady Rong.
- Young Lady Rong.

256
00:12:49,426 --> 00:12:50,560
- Here's to you.
- Let's go.

257
00:12:50,560 --> 00:12:51,560
That's too kind of you.

258
00:12:51,610 --> 00:12:53,280
Remember to enjoy yourselves here.

259
00:12:53,280 --> 00:12:54,693
- Sure.
- Thanks, Young Lady Rong.

260
00:12:58,737 --> 00:12:59,520
Young Lady Rong.

261
00:12:59,640 --> 00:13:00,370
I'll be going.

262
00:13:00,880 --> 00:13:01,490
I'm leaving.

263
00:13:01,680 --> 00:13:02,800
Young Lady Rong.

264
00:13:09,411 --> 00:13:12,280
(Tavern)

265
00:13:12,370 --> 00:13:14,680
Split up for patrols.
Nothing is allowed to happen.

266
00:13:15,160 --> 00:13:16,040
Young Master Lin!

267
00:13:17,010 --> 00:13:17,880
Young Master Lin!

268
00:13:17,880 --> 00:13:20,426
Something's happened to the winery
on the west side of the city.

269
00:13:21,280 --> 00:13:22,090
Young Master Lin!

270
00:13:24,026 --> 00:13:25,090
What's wrong with you?

271
00:13:25,090 --> 00:13:25,640
Sorry.

272
00:13:25,915 --> 00:13:27,400
I'm in a hurry to see my young master.

273
00:13:28,160 --> 00:13:28,680
Wait.

274
00:13:28,800 --> 00:13:30,330
What's going on at the winery?

275
00:13:30,337 --> 00:13:31,330
I went to make a delivery

276
00:13:31,337 --> 00:13:32,826
and found out something was wrong.

277
00:13:32,848 --> 00:13:34,226
The carriage wasn't carrying wine.

278
00:13:34,450 --> 00:13:35,040
But...

279
