371
00:19:56,448 --> 00:19:57,250
Look over there.

372
00:19:57,337 --> 00:19:58,160
It's so beautiful.

373
00:19:58,930 --> 00:19:59,730
It's so crowded.

374
00:19:59,730 --> 00:20:00,840
It's so lively today.

375
00:20:02,890 --> 00:20:04,120
Slow down.

376
00:20:07,250 --> 00:20:09,840
Come on. Come here.

377
00:20:10,040 --> 00:20:10,760
Be careful.

378
00:20:15,160 --> 00:20:17,271
With Young Master Lin
guarding the checkpoint,

379
00:20:17,280 --> 00:20:18,490
