444
00:23:17,170 --> 00:23:18,520
I ran into your friend, Feng Ming.

445
00:23:18,737 --> 00:23:20,520
Someone was assassinated
in a back alley.

446
00:23:20,693 --> 00:23:23,182
This flower fair is not going to be
a peaceful one tonight.

447
00:23:23,226 --> 00:23:25,840
And Jiang Ruhai,
something's wrong with him too.

448
00:23:26,410 --> 00:23:27,010
I got it.

449
00:23:28,250 --> 00:23:29,840
How come you don't seem nervous at all?

450
00:23:30,520 --> 00:23:31,600
