477
00:24:44,840 --> 00:24:46,250
Wanci, aren't you feeling unwell?

478
00:24:46,250 --> 00:24:47,170
Why are you here?

479
00:24:47,170 --> 00:24:48,660
Shukuang was injured, lost her memory

480
00:24:48,737 --> 00:24:49,490
