481
00:24:49,515 --> 00:24:51,250
She can't play
Flying Flower Order with you.

482
00:24:51,271 --> 00:24:53,004
Let me be the keeper of this checkpoint.

483
00:24:53,120 --> 00:24:53,890
That's fine.

484
00:24:56,120 --> 00:24:57,800
