514
00:27:03,080 --> 00:27:03,600
Yu,

515
00:27:03,600 --> 00:27:04,520
that's not fair.

516
00:27:04,520 --> 00:27:05,493
None of your business!

517
00:27:12,293 --> 00:27:13,760
Young Lady Lin has disappeared.

518
00:27:13,804 --> 00:27:14,982
The carriage is still there.

519
00:27:33,970 --> 00:27:35,800
Why is the Yellow-Robed here?

520
00:28:10,671 --> 00:28:12,715
Yan Shao, please ascend the building.

521
00:28:13,840 --> 00:28:14,520
Thank you.

522
00:28:17,137 --> 00:28:18,582
