ever treated you badly?

549
00:29:49,490 --> 00:29:50,040
No.

550
00:29:51,040 --> 00:29:52,840
What will happen
when the flower ball drops?

551
00:29:53,450 --> 00:29:54,520
I can't tell you.

552
00:29:54,715 --> 00:29:56,515
